HEADWORD: Cervus
<hw>Cer"vus</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a
deer.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A genus of ruminants, including the
red deer and other allied species.</def>⟦br⟧
